              <h3 class='entry-title'><a href="/draft/rest-less-on-the-web">REST-less on the Web</a></h3>
              <div class='entry-content'>
                <p>In Merb, my preferred routing is this:</p>
                
                <pre><code>r.match(  "/:controller/:id/:action").to({})&#x000A;r.match(%r{/:controller/(\d+)}      ).to(:action =&gt; "show", :id =&gt; "[2]")&#x000A;r.match(  "/:controller/:action"    ).to({})&#x000A;r.match(  "/:controller"            ).to(:action =&gt; "index")&#x000A;</code></pre>
              </div>
